README.md
     8‚Üí# Overview
    10‚Üí`once_cell` provides two new cell-like types, `unsync::OnceCell` and `sync::OnceCell`. `OnceCell`
    11‚Üímight store arbitrary non-`Copy` types, can be assigned to at most once and provide direct access
    12‚Üíto the stored contents. In a nutshell, API looks *roughly* like this:
    13‚Üí
    14‚Üí```rust
